  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What happened to the principal who attacked the student",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna - The Jaffna District Child Protection Authority has initiated investigations regarding a 14-year-old student being assaulted and injured by the principal in a school located in Nallur area.",
        "A 14-year-old student from Nallur Vinayagar Road has been injured in this incident.",
        "According to initial investigations, the principal assaulted the student after he told him that he was not doing the work he was told to do.",
        "It was reported that the student suffered an injury on his forehead and was physically and mentally affected.",
        "Subsequently, the court refused to grant bail to the principal, who was brought before the court under the Animal Cruelty Act, and ordered him to be remanded for 14 days. (R.)"
      ],
